<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday My Love</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <script src="script.js" defer></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            animation: fadeIn 2s;
        }
        .heart-animation {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('images/hearts.gif');
            background-size: cover;
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }
        .next-step {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #ff4d6d;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .next-step:hover {
            background: #e63e5a;
        }
        .memories {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .memories img {
            width: 30%;
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .special-images {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .special-images img {
            width: 40%;
            max-width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="heart-animation"></div>

    <div id="home" class="container">
        <h1>Happy Birthday My Love ‚ù§Ô∏è</h1>
        <p>You make my world brighter every day!</p>
        <img src="images/cute-heart.jpg" alt="Cute Heart">
        <button class="next-step" onclick="showPage('memories')">Do you want to see what's next? üíñ</button>
    </div>

    <div id="memories" class="container hidden">
        <h2>Some Beautiful Memories</h2>
         <div class="memories">
            <img src="images/memory1.jpg" alt="Memory 1">
            <img src="images/memory8.jpeg" alt="Memory 2">
            <img src="images/image7.jpg" alt="Memory 3">
            <img src="images/image5.jpg" alt="Memory 4">
            <img src="images/image6.jpeg" alt="Memory 5">
            <img src="images/image4.jpeg" alt="Memory 6">
        </div>
        <button class="next-step" onclick="showPage('notes')">Want to read something special? üíå</button>
    </div>

    <div id="notes" class="container hidden">
        <h2>Love Notes Just for You üíå</h2>
        <p>My love, every day with you is a gift. Your smile lights up my world, your laughter is my favorite melody. No matter what happens, I will always cherish and love you with all my heart. ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>
        <button class="next-step" onclick="showPage('game')">Let's play a little game! üéÆ</button>
    </div>

    <div id="game" class="container hidden">
        <h2>Guess the Memory! üß†‚ù§Ô∏è</h2>
        <p>Select the correct answer for each memory!</p>
        <div>
            <p>1. Where did we go from where it all started?? ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Correct! It was our magical first date! ü•∞')">WET and JOY</button>
            <button onclick="alert('Oops! Try again! üòò')">Tekdi</button>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>2. Where did I kissed you? üíñ</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Correct! The most special moment! üòç')">In Car</button>
            <button onclick="alert('Oops! Not quite! üòÜ')">In haunted house</button>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>3. What was our first movie together? üé¨</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Yes! We laughed so much! ‚ù§Ô∏è')">Crime/Drama</button>
            <button onclick="alert('Nope! But nice try! üòò')">Action</button>
        </div>
        <button class="next-step" onclick="showPage('music')">Time for some music! üé∂</button>
    </div>

    <div id="music" class="container hidden">
        <h2>Pick A Song For Us üé∂</h2>
        <p>Choose a song to make this moment even more special!</p>
        <select id="music-select">
            <option value="music/1.mp3">Our Love Song 1</option>
            <option value="music/2.mp3">Our Love Song 2</option>
            <option value="music/jhol.mp3">A Special Surprise Song</option>
        </select>
        <audio id="player" controls></audio>
        <button class="next-step" onclick="showPage('surprise')">One last surprise! üéÅ</button>
    </div>

    <div id="surprise" class="container hidden">
        <h2>A Special Message Just for You ‚ù§Ô∏è</h2>
        <p>My love for you grows every second, every minute, every day! You are my sunshine, my happiness, my everything! üíï</p>
        <div class="special-images">
            <img src="images/image3.jpeg" alt="Special Image 1">
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showPage(page) {
            document.querySelectorAll('.container').forEach(div => div.classList.add('hidden'));
            document.getElementById(page).classList.remove('hidden');
        }
        document.getElementById("music-select").addEventListener("change", function() {
            document.getElementById("player").src = this.value;
            document.getElementById("player").play();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
